quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  76,23,"D Nekwni, s tidep, i k id Issersen Leqwôan, s lmizan"
  76,24,"Eûbeô i uêuddu n Mass ik; segsen, ur teccev, ur jehhel"
  76,25,"Mmekti d isem n Mass ik, tafrara, tameddit"
  76,26,"Deg iv, knu yaS, u sbuccaâ iT tallit $wezzifen"
  76,27,"Ih, wigi êemmlen taêemmaqt, stehzan deg wass amôay"
  76,28,"Nekwni Nxelq iten, Nesseohed i$san nnsen. Ma ihwa ya£, a Nerr ay ten icban, wakali, deg umkan nnsen"
  76,29,"Wagi, s tidep, d asmekti. Win ib$an, ad iddem abrid ar Mass is"
  76,30,"Ur tbeqqum, siwa ma Ib$a Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab"
  76,31,"Win i S ihwan, a t Issekcem ar uêunu S; ma d imednas, Ihegga yasen aâaqeb aqeôêan"